Author: lbvl
Text: Here with you both, it feels like being stuck and feeling like you don’t belong at the same time. It is draining. Stay strong, only thing that helps is time and giving yourself some space to work things out one by one. They are big, but break them in littke pieces, one at a time <3

Author: _leastofthese_
Text: I am in the exact same place dude. And I’m coping the same way. I wish I had magic words of wisdom, but I can say that I’m with you and we deserve to thrive ❤️
